Darah Emas.

16
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,360
Kau masih ingat.

17
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,680
Salah satu teknik rahasia
Heluo berlatih emas.

18
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,800
Praktisinya akan seperti
memakai baju zirah.

19
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,920
Tenggorokan keras seperti besi.

20
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,640
Pasti adalah orang hebat.

21
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,360
Minggir.

22
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,280
Jangan harap!

23
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,480
Guru.

24
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,960
Jurus pembunuh ini sangat aneh.

25
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,880
Haishi, kau harus hati-hati.

26
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,800
Kaisar, tangkap pedangnya!

27
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,560
Sesuai aturan padang rumput.

28
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,920
Bergulat saja.

29
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:23,120
Kaisar, cepat pergi.

30
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:23,840
Tidak.

31
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,720
Katanya sekarang Praktisi Emas,
Pemanggil Angin…

32
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,940
…sudah tak ada di dunia ini lagi.

33
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,120
Ternyata pewarisnya
dari suku luar.

34
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,400
Apa kau tak merasa ini menarik?

35
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,240
Lindungi Kaisar.

36
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,920
Bunuh aku.

37
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,800
Berikan aku kehormatan prajurit.

38
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,240
Sampai jumpa di akhirat.

39
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,320
Sampai jumpa di akhirat.

40
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:36,760
Kaisar.

41
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,440
Kalian berjasa melindungiku.

42
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:44,920
Katakanlah.

43
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,800
Mau hadiah apa?

44
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,240
Saya takut melebihi batas.

45
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,960
Asalkan ada di negara ini,
kau boleh ambil semua.

46
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,720
Kalau begitu, saya tak sungkan lagi.

47
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,320
Jangan!

48
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,320
Jianming!

49
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:07,800
Guru!

50
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,200
Adipati!

51
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,080
Jianming.

52
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,040
Di dunia ini tak ada Zhuoying.

53
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,440
Aku Duohan!

54
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,480
Tangkap dia.

55
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:23,600
Baik.

56
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:34,280
Kaisar.

57
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,320
Saya merawat murid pengkhianat.

58
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,440
Kaisar.

59
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,480
Zhuoying…

60
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,799
Zhuoying pasti punya kesulitan.

61
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:41,760
Jianming.

62
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,320
Kau lagi-lagi melindungiku.

63
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:50,990
Kau bilang Istana Jincheng
adalah istana tanpa bayangan.

64
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,160
Apa pun tak bisa disembunyikan.

65
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,360
Namun, tak diduga,…

66
00:08:56,680 --> 00:09:00,600
…lentera terang di sisimulah
yang mau membunuhmu.

67
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,640
Untuk apa memaksa?

68
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,480
Hanya demi janji itu?

69
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,560
Lepaskanlah.

70
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,560
Kau sudah tak berutang padaku lagi.

71
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,760
Guru.

72
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,560
Bawa kembali Zhuoying.

73
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,840
Jika tak bisa, bunuh dia.

74
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,480
Guru.

75
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,880
Bunuh Fang Zhuoying.

76
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,360
Dia terlalu gila.

77
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,200
Takutnya orang lain
tak bisa melawannya.

78
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,040
Namun, kau bisa.

79
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,320
Dia kakakmu.

80
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,640
Dia pasti akan mengalah padamu.

81
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,560
Adipati.

82
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:54,480
Setelah luka ini sudah diurus,
kelak harus berhati-hati.

83
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,640
Saya rebus obat untuk Anda,
saya segera kembali.

84
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,480
Tuan Haishi.

85
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,480
Guru.

86
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:22,300
Sebenarnya kau sudah bunuh
berapa banyak orang?

87
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,120
Tak terhitung.

88
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,680
Kapan terakhir kali Anda
bunuh orang?

89
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,900
Pemberontakan Tuan Putri palsu.

90
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,960
Kau bohong.

91
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:38,280
Kemarin, kau baru membunuh Zhe Liu.

92
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:43,200
Pengawal Gelap bilang kau
pindahkan semua orang Divisi Sulam.

93
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,800
Kau bicara dengan Zhe Liu.

94
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,040
Kau membunuhnya
dalam beberapa kata.

95
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:52,120
Su Yi juga sudah kau bunuh, 'kan?

96
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,000
Coba tebak, sebelum dia mati,…

97
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:00,720
…apa dia akan mengutukmu
mati dengan mengenaskan?

98
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,960
Kau minta Zhuoying
melakukan apa untukmu?

99
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,960
Zhuoying lebih mementingkan
janji dari nyawanya.

100
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:13,720
Sejak diasuh dan mengikutimu
sampai sekarang,…

101
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:17,840
…apa dia pernah melawan perintahmu?

102
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:20,980
Jika Zhe Liu bunuh diri setelah
pulang dari Kediaman Raja Chang,…

103
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:24,600
…Zhuoying mau balas dendam
juga harus mencari Raja Chang.

104
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,680
Tak mungkin mencari Kaisar.

105
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,000
Guru.

106
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,600
Apa ini benar-benar ulahmu?

107
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,760
Kenapa Zhe Liu harus mati?

108
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,960
Dia hanyalah wanita buta
yang kesepian.

109
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:46,120
Zhuoying mencintainya,
seperti mencintai nyawanya.

110
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:51,240
Zhe Liu sudah mati,
Zhuoying menangis sangat keras.

111
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,800
Mungkin seumur hidupnya
tak bisa menangis lagi.

112
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,480
Karena itu, wanita buta
ini harus mati.

113
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:04,400
Jika dia tak mati, Zhuoying
akan punya kelemahan.

114
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:13,720
Guru.

115
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:18,960
Selamanya Anda tak akan
punya kelemahan, 'kan?

116
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:23,700
Apa yang mau kau katakan?

117
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:32,680
Zhuoying dan aku seperti
saudara, seperti teman.

118
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:35,640
Kami bisa minum bersama
dan saling bepergian.

119
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,360
Dekat seperti saudara kandung.

120
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:39,160
Anda adalah guru saya.

121
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,080
Anda…

122
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,200
Guru, Anda sangat berhati dingin.

123
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,560
Meski Zhe Liu,…

124
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:55,800
…meski Zhuoying,…

125
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:59,640
…meski orang yang bersumpah
akan selalu setia pada Anda,…

126
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,800
…juga seperti bidak di tangan Anda.

127
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:04,560
Bisa dilepaskan kapan pun, 'kan?

128
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:12,200
Tuan Haishi.

129
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,440
Kabar dari istana.

130
00:13:13,540 --> 00:13:14,940
Pasukan Dazheng sudah berkumpul.

131
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,520
Didesak untuk segera berangkat.

132
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,920
Jawab mereka.

133
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,480
Tuan Haishi segera pergi.

134
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:21,760
Baik.

135
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:26,400
Guru.

136
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,720
Apakah Anda membesarkan kami…

137
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,440
…demi melihat kami saling membunuh?

138
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:39,790
Sebenarnya seberapa banyak saya
bisa memercayai Anda?

139
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:16,840
Tuan Fang.

140
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,360
Pengkhianat Duohan
sembunyi di gubuk ini.

141
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:04,960
Aku tahu kau punya titah Kaisar.

142
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,600
Marilah.

143
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:26,440
Tuan Fang.

144
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,840
Luka Anda tak parah, 'kan?

145
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,480
Fang Jianming ini…

146
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,520
…memang hebat.

147
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:39,840
Membunuh dua Jenderal Huku
yang hebat.

148
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:43,440
Raja, apa ada tindakan selanjutnya?

149
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:47,400
Jika membunuh Di Xu
dan Fang Jianming…

150
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:49,160
…tak bisa dilakukan satu orang,…

151
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,080
…aku hanya bisa kerahkan
pasukan besar…

152
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,700
…dan berusaha sekuat tenaga.

153
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:57,160
Apa Raja ingin menyerang
Perbatasan Huangquan?

154
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,840
Apa sudah hubungi
mata-mata Su Ming?

155
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,760
Sudah.

156
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,680
Dia mau bantu kita membalaskan
dendam Su Ming.

157
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:09,000
Namun, Perbatasan Huangquan 
mudah dijaga sulit diserang.

158
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:14,160
Aku tahu maksudmu.

159
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,800
Aku juga tak mau habiskan
banyak pasukan.

160
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,560
Jadi, Raja…

161
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,400
Raja Chang…

162
00:16:21,810 --> 00:16:23,860
…mau bekerja sama denganku
menyerang Kota Tianqi.

163
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:26,570
Namun, sekarang sudah
musim gugur.

164
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:28,520
Musim dingin akan tiba.

165
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:31,720
Bukan waktu tepat
untuk menyerang.

166
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,270
Aku sudah diskusi dengannya.

167
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:37,520
Tunggu setelah musim semi tiba,…

168
00:16:38,920 --> 00:16:40,360
…dia buat masalah di kota.

169
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:43,180
Aku menyerang
Perbatasan Huangquan dari luar.

170
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,400
Kita bekerja sama luar dan dalam.

171
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,880
Taklukkan Dazheng.

172
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:52,480
Ternyata Tuan Fang datang
ke Perbatasan Huangquan…

173
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,800
…karena situasi ini.

174
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:55,800
Tuan Fang.

175
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,240
Ini sudah siang.

176
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,600
Namun, dari 10 pengintai tak ada
yang kembali.

177
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:03,360
Lagi pula, di padang rumput sudah
bunyi dua kali suara peringatan.

178
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:04,880
Setelah itu, tak ada kabar lagi.

179
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,960
Sepuluh orang ini mungkin
sudah dibunuh.

180
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:10,590
Adipati Qinghai mencegah
orang lama buat masalah,…

181
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:13,240
…500 pasukan yang keluar kota
tak dipilih dari Pengawal Gelap.

182
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,100
Melainkan dipilih dari
Pasukan Utara.

183
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:18,440
Katanya kebanyakan adalah
bawahan yang pernah…

184
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,280
…dipimpin Tuan Fu di Kamp Huangquan.

185
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,790
Namun, Tuan Fang membawa
mereka mengejar setengah bulan.

186
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:23,840
Beberapa kali mengepung.

187
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,640
Fang Zhuoying hanya sendirian.

188
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,119
Keberadaannya tak bisa ditebak.

189
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:30,360
Dari Zhongzhou ke Hanzhou,
jaraknya 500 kilometer.

190
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,380
Tak bisa menangkapnya.

191
00:17:31,600 --> 00:17:33,520
Malah mengorbankan
beberapa prajurit kuat.

192
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:36,400
Sekarang Fang Zhuoying
melewati Gunung Piluo,…

193
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,400
…10 orang terbunuh lagi.

194
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,960
Sepertinya dia sulit
untuk ditangkap.

195
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:45,040
Sekarang dia sudah masuk
wilayah Jiaman.

196
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:47,690
Empat ratus pasukan
berkuda yang tersisa,…

197
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:50,200
…bukan utusan, juga bukan pedagang.

198
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:53,040
Tak bisa masuk ke dalam
wilayah suku lain.

199
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:58,280
Aku dan Tuan Fu akan
menyamar dan masuk.

200
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,240
Tuan Fang.

201
00:18:01,120 --> 00:18:03,600
Serahkan masalah penangkapan
Fang Zhuoying padaku.

202
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:04,320
Tak boleh.

203
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,560
Guru serahkan hal ini padaku.

204
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:08,000
Harus aku yang lakukan.

205
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:10,800
Kau tinggal di Kamp Huangquan.

206
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:11,960
Kapan berangkat?

207
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,160
Segera.

208
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:19,360
Apa itu dia?

209
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:22,000
Seharusnya iya.

210
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,160
Tuan, lihat!

211
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:24,200
Itu orang Huku.

212
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:32,640
Tuan.

213
00:20:32,910 --> 00:20:34,780
Jika pengkhianat masuk
ke dalam pasukan Huku,…

214
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:35,980
…maka semua sudah terlambat.

215
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,840
Tak disangka pengkhianat ini
bersekongkol dengan pasukan Huku.

216
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:43,640
Di saat ini, mungkin hanya panah
Tuan Fang baru bisa mengejar.

217
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:47,320
Biar kucoba.

218
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,040
Zhuoying.

219
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,480
Ini adalah taruhan terakhir kita.

220
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:42,440
Jika kau percaya hubungan
Haishi padamu,…

221
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:45,880
…percaya dia lebih baik melawan
perintah juga tak akan membunuhmu.

222
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,960
Kita bertaruh di sini.

223
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,960
Jika kau menang,
kau dapatkan kebebasan…

224
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,880
…dan juga 7.000 mil Hanzhou.

225
00:21:56,120 --> 00:21:57,200
Aku tak akan menghindar.

226
00:21:57,840 --> 00:22:00,160
Panahmu ini harus tepat.

227
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:01,720
Aku percaya padamu.

228
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,280
Pasti tepat sasaran.

229
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:06,580
(Kamp Huangquan)

230
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,200
Tuan Fang.

231
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:10,360
Kau tak mau istirahat
beberapa hari?

232
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:13,520
Ada Tuan Fu yang akan
melapor ke Kota Tianqi.

233
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:15,120
Benar.

234
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:15,960
Tuan Fang.

235
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,200
Lukamu belum sembuh.

